Step 1:
Make a zipfile of the auto_indexer folder or download the zipfile.

Step 2:
Convert the zipfile to tar.gz or download the tar.gz

Step 3:
Upload t he tar.gz to a site and enter the address in drupal cms interface.
Extend -> add new moudle -> add from url -> enable newly added moudules, continue -> select auto index and install -> configuration -> search pages -> edit, automatically index on create/upload of content, save search page.

Enjoy